      • contextChanged

        protected abstract void contextChanged(ContextEvent<T> event)
        The callback method which gets called when the content for the action command type in the application wide context changes. To get the latest content use something like: Collection<? extends T> myActionCommands = getApplicationContext().findAll(event.getType());
        Parameters:
